casebody.data:
Susan V. KLAT, petitioner,
v.
MITCHELL REPAIR INFORMATION COMPANY, LLC, et al. No. 13-6428. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 12, 2013. Case below, 528 Fed.Appx. 733 . Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
